name: Giant Santa Toy Sacks
description:
As a special limited edition, Hope & Rainbows are happy to introduce these fantastic giant Santa toy sacks as an ideal alternative to the traditional Christmas stocking. Emblazoned with a colourful image of Santa, surrounded by pretty pale blue snowflakes, one of these bags would provide enough room for even the largest of princess castles or dump-trucks that may be on your little one's wish list.

Made from crisp white cotton, these bags measure an enormous 60 x 76 cm (considerably bigger than a standard pillowcase). They have a strong, long hanging loop in one corner and a double-drawstring closure.

Original artwork and photography. © 2013 Kate Hope, Hope & Rainbows.

name: Baby & Children's Personalised Tote Bag - Party Bag - Shoe Bag (set of 10)
description:
Due to popular demand, all Hope & Rainbows images are now also available on these adorable little childrens' sized tote bags. 

The image is heat transferred onto one side of a white cotton flat tote bag (measuring 21cm x 26cm), creating a beautiful reusable personalised party bag, a unique and individual shoe bag, or the most original and effective gift wrapping for a special present.

Bags available individually for £3.50 (can be ordered through each image listing).
A set of 10 bags available for a discounted £30.00.

Sets of 10 bags can either display one image (e.g. a princess or cowboy) with the individual children's names on each, or be personalised to match each child's name. Please provide a list of each name required, along with the image for each, at checkout.

Original artwork and photography. © 2013 Kate Hope, Hope & Rainbows.

name: Bespoke Alphabet Print
description:
While I build up a full gallery of all alphabet letters, if you require a personalised print that doesn't already appear in my shop, please purchase this item and let me know both the name of the child you would like this to be printed for, as well as their gender and any preference you may have for a particular image.  I will do my very best to accommodate your requirements!

This print has been designed digitally and will be professionally printed on thick, quality stock.

Choose from three formats; mounted (12" x 16"), framed (12" x 16") or a pack of 20 postcards.

Your chosen product(s) will be beautifully and carefully wrapped in brown paper and tied with pretty string, ready to gift to someone special!

Please let me know the name of the child you would like this to be printed for at checkout.

name: A is for Aeroplane

Your chosen product(s) will then be beautifully and carefully wrapped in brown paper and tied with pretty string, ready to gift to someone special!
